This PR caused a breaking change in `@azure/identity` from `4.10.1` to `4.10.2`:

**Before:**
```jsonc
// npm show @azure/identity@4.10.1 --json | jq '.engines'
{
  "node": ">=18.0.0"
}
```

**After:**
```jsonc
// npm show @azure/identity@4.10.2 --json | jq '.engines'
{
  "node": ">=20.0.0"
}
```
